title: Independent Candidate Wajid Hussain Khan wins PS- 92 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent, Candidate Wajid Hussain Khan has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-92, Korangi-III, by securing 28,276 votes.
According to unofficial result issued by Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Mirza Farhan Baig of Jamat e Islami (JI), who bagged votes 20,830.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 32.81 %.
